# dev setup on MES5

1) install MES5 + mirrors + updates
2) urpmi subversion python-django python-IPy
3) svn co svn+ssh://login@svn.mandriva.com/svn/private/corporate/soft/mmc-wizard mmc-wizard
in two terms :
4) cd mmc-wizard/branches/wizard-2/agent/; ./simple-agent.py (XML-RPC agent)
6) cd mmc-wizard/branches/wizard-2/www/; 
7) ./manage.py syncdb --noinput (create DB for the first time)
8) ./manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:8000 (run web server)
9) with your web browser go to http://SRV_IP:8000
10) login password : root password
